      highlights: [
        "After Hurricane Katrina, a hidden weapon of mass destruction, a secret Nuclear Silo, emerges under the barren desert, detected sharply by the UN’s KH-11 satellite. The United Nations and allied forces quickly deployed soldiers to capture mysterious nuclear silo. Commander, prepare your army for the tough battle ahead! Good luck!",
        "Desert Storm is a weekly event, where you engage in a war against another alliance with a comparable battle power in a dedicated battlefield (at first game stages it will be an alliance of your server, later on of a different server).",
        "It is one of the most enjoyable events of the game, because of its dynamics and its rewards ( Honor points , accelerators, resources, decoration chests, dieletric ceramic). Additionally you will not lose troops you use in this battle.",
        "The drawbacks are that not all members of the alliance can participate, but lately the A-B task force feature was introduced, bringing the possibility to deploy up to 60 members in the event : 20 starting participants and 10 substitutes for each task force."
      ],
