      title: "Season 1 – The Crimson Plague: Virus-Infested World, New Features, Resources, and Alliance cross-server warfare",
      description: "Last War Season 1 - The Crimson Plague features a new infected world map, Virus Resistance system, professions, hero upgrades, exclusive weapons, new buildings, resources, and cross-server territory wars.",
      category: "seasons",
      sourcePath: "season-1-the-crimson-plague/index.html",
