      description: "At the end of ☀️ Season 3 – Golden Kingdom the game will enter an off-season phase, during which Season 3 – Celebration will start.This time the Season 3 Celebration menu will be available starting from day 7 of week 8 of Season 3, and the Celebration will continue for 5 weeks. Icon of Season 3 Celebration: Contents Celebration TimelineWeek",
