        "Icon of Season 3 Celebration:",
        "We can immediately see that some of the well known events of celebration will come back: Transfer Surge, Bingo Task, Black Market and the Champion Duel. The main difference is that the rewards change, bringing more overlord related items.",
        "The first week focuses on the Transfer Surge. Players can now transfer to other servers. While this Transfer Surge event is similar to previous ones, a key change is that the Warzone Score will now be considered, determining the number of commanders who can join a warzone."
