      slug: "vip-program",
      title: "Last War VIP Program: Activation, Levels and Rewards. Find out the Best Strategy, investing your diamonds, for powerful buffs.",
      description: "Last War VIP Program explained: discover VIP levels, rewards, costs, and practical tips to maximize diamond value and accelerate your growth.",
      category: "progression",
